## 6. Dynamic AI Generative Flows (Phase 6.6)
- **AI Skill Sandbox**: Built a dedicated Genkit testing environment directly inside the [ai-skills](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Development/STANDLO/standlo.com/admin/app/ai-skills) Admin Portal. Admins can tweak the AI logic and test it instantly without triggering real Firestore lifecycle updates.
- **Mock Context Injection**: Integrated a structural `mockPayloadJson` parameter inside the schema that gets persisted on save. This pre-fills the execution context (`{{ data.document }}`) for immediate testing.
- **Strict JSON Generation**: Tightened the Zod JSON-schema rules injected into Genkit for arrays and translations ensuring deterministic LLM output parsing.
- **API Keys & Emulators**: Wired the Genkit [getAi](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Development/STANDLO/standlo.com/functions/src/genkit/index.ts#11-24) initialization to the `geminiApiKey` secret, testing it locally via [.secret.local](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Development/STANDLO/standlo.com/functions/.secret.local) and `gcloud` while protecting the repository via [.gitignore](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Development/STANDLO/standlo.com/.gitignore).
- **Validation**: Performed a full-monorepo validation run (`root`, `admin`, `functions`) fixing all transient ESLint errors ensuring 100% `0 vulnerabilities`, `0 warnings`, `0 errors` on build.
